    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. The 6 non-assessed factors are consistent with MRL 2 scope per ASME V&V 40 Table 3. The CFD model is accepted for use in identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. The relative hemolysis index RH = 0.83 satisfies the RH < 1 acceptance criterion across all evaluated operating points. Supporting methodology is further documented in the peer-reviewed literature (see referencesIdentifier).",
